The two side catches are mounted on the grey metal bracket that the seat =
itself screws to.  They are spring loaded so that they latch in place =
and are stamped metal.  They're about 4 inches long and from the end are =
U shaped (see ascii art). =20

They sort of look like this from the side.  The break in the =3D is =
where it engages with the pin.
___________________
