=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D  =3D=3D=3D=3D		=09

From the end they are U Shaped, with the open end facing down.

These pieces are mentioned in the 70 Westy manual =
(http://www.thesamba.com/vw/type2/photos/stoermer/70westymanpage7.jpg)

